overview.en: The 1895Chain is blockchain system is an open source project in the global blockchain initiated by the 1895 foundation, which is a BaaS project consisting of a micro kernel, a chain operating system, functional modules, and a growing number of private cloud storage hardware devices located all over the world.
overview.zh: 1895Chain 是借助区块链技术和广告智能合约设计的Web生态公链,将有效解决互联网广告存在的诸多问题,开发者可以依托开放的公链接口开发独立的浏览器,odin token是全生态中唯一可以流转的价值载体.
